summary: A concept the Japanese Anime-"Chuka Ichiban! "
descriptionHtml:
Hey there, It's Martin"Ram"Wu again :P

"中華一番!(Chuka Ichiban!) "
Some introduction of Chuka Ichiban! in Wikipedia-[url=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ch%C5%ABka_Ichiban!]https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ch%C5%ABka_Ichiban![/url]
